title: Franco Ristorante
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Pizza, Italian, Beer/Wine, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A family friendly Italian food restaurant that offers Daiya brand vegan cheese for pizza and dinner entrees in place of dairy cheese, made to order. Gluten free pizza, pasta, and beer also available. Try the broccoli rabe saute in garlic and olive oil. Has Wi-Fi and Italian music played in the background.
